      <p class="text-xs text-amber-600 font-semibold mt-1">Additional $129 activation fee required</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
      <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Stocks – One Step Challenge</p>
      <p>Account sizes of $25K or $50K with fees from $99 to $249. Requires a 7% profit target with a 2% daily pause and 5% maximum drawdown. Profit share is 70%.</p>
